HEADWORD: 21
<hw>21</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>one more than twenty;
twenty plus one more; denoting a quantity consisting of twenty-one items
or units; -- representing the number twenty-one as Arabic
numerals</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> twenty-one, xxi</syn>⟦br⟧
